{"id":98939,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2010/08/诗悼舟曲/","date":"2010-08-17T14:59:33Z","modified":"2010-08-17T14:59:33Z","title":"诗悼舟曲","content":"<p>泥石呼啸出深山, 偌大县城吞半边. 人在泥中活命少, 楼于石下靖节难. 乡民伐树包稍鼓, 远客攫金囊滚圆. 致富梦如肥皂泡,天堂坠落入深渊.<br />\n(<img alt=\"\" src=\"http://news.wap.sohu.com/images3/upload/book/blog/20081030001.gif\" /><a href=\"http://goto.sms.sohu.com/goto.php?aid=198&#038;pid=1622\">手机看博客</a>)</p>\n<p>“要翻墙，<a href=\"http://idiaoyuzhifa.info\" target=\"_blank\">用赛风”</a>.</p>\n","author":176,"categories":[1],"tags":[8800]}